{"thag9.1:0.1":"Theragatha 9.1 ","thag9.1:0.2":"Navakanipata ","thag9.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag9.1:0.4":"Bhutattheragatha ","thag9.1:1.1":"“Yada dukkham jaramarananti pandito, ","thag9.1:1.2":"Aviddasu yattha sita puthujjana; ","thag9.1:1.3":"Dukkham parinnaya satova jhayati, ","thag9.1:1.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:2.1":"Yada dukkhassavahanim visattikam, ","thag9.1:2.2":"Papancasanghatadukhadhivahinim; ","thag9.1:2.3":"Tanham pahantvana satova jhayati, ","thag9.1:2.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:3.1":"Yada sivam dvecaturangagaminam, ","thag9.1:3.2":"Magguttamam sabbakilesasodhanam; ","thag9.1:3.3":"Pannaya passitva satova jhayati, ","thag9.1:3.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:4.1":"Yada asokam virajam asankhatam, ","thag9.1:4.2":"Santam padam sabbakilesasodhanam; ","thag9.1:4.3":"Bhaveti samyojanabandhanacchidam, ","thag9.1:4.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:5.1":"Yada nabhe gajjati meghadundubhi, ","thag9.1:5.2":"Dharakula vihagapathe samantato; ","thag9.1:5.3":"Bhikkhu ca pabbharagatova jhayati, ","thag9.1:5.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:6.1":"Yada nadinam kusumakulanam, ","thag9.1:6.2":"Vicitta-vaneyya-vatamsakanam; ","thag9.1:6.3":"Tire nisinno sumanova jhayati, ","thag9.1:6.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:7.1":"Yada nisithe rahitamhi kanane, ","thag9.1:7.2":"Deve galantamhi nadanti dathino; ","thag9.1:7.3":"Bhikkhu ca pabbharagatova jhayati, ","thag9.1:7.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:8.1":"Yada vitakke uparundhiyattano, ","thag9.1:8.2":"Nagantare nagavivaram samassito; ","thag9.1:8.3":"Vitaddaro vitakhilova jhayati, ","thag9.1:8.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati. ","thag9.1:9.1":"Yada sukhi malakhilasokanasano, ","thag9.1:9.2":"Niraggalo nibbanatho visallo; ","thag9.1:9.3":"Sabbasave byantikatova jhayati, ","thag9.1:9.4":"Tato ratim paramataram na vindati”ti. ","thag9.1:9.5":"… Bhuto thero … ","thag9.1:9.6":"Navakanipato nitthito. ","thag9.1:10.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag9.1:10.1":"Bhuto tathaddaso thero, ","thag9.1:10.2":"eko khaggavisanava; ","thag9.1:10.3":"Navakamhi nipatamhi, ","thag9.1:10.4":"gathayopi ima navati. "}